{"tid":2482022,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳蕾《荒島之幻象》大解構","createTime":"2021-04-09T16:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T10:11:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf01148160ebf83144909309cb1d296705f60c1","tid":2482022,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"#陳蕾 #Panther #荒島之幻象<br />\n<br />\n陳蕾《荒島之幻象》大解構<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Snkl6Tllbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8Snkl6Tllbo&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=0516a0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Snkl6Tllbo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nwarnermusichk<br />\n188K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n兩個人流落荒島，呢一種浪漫會唔會只係一種幻象，只係將身邊嘅事物浪漫化？🤔<br />\n即刻聽陳蕾講解呢首歌嘅創作理念啦‼️🏝<br />\n<br />\n#陳蕾​ #Panther​ #荒島之幻象​ #IllusionOfADesertIsland​<br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n陳蕾 親自曲詞作品 《荒島之幻象》<br />\n荒島中有你伴我蹉跎 哪怕只是短暫的幻象<br />\n<br />\nListen: <a href=\"https://PantherChan.lnk.to/IllusionOf...​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2FPantherChan.lnk.to%2FIllusionOf...%E2%80%8B&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=7989a5a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://PantherChan.lnk.to/IllusionOf...​</a><br />\n<br />\n曲：陳蕾<br />\n詞：陳蕾<br />\n編：蔡德才@人山人海<br />\n監：蔡德才@人山人海<br />\n<br />\n失血中的傷口 沾污了我雙手<br />\n儘管得救 怕只怕 洗不走<br />\n心中那裂痕隨之將身體解剖<br />\n<br />\n得你碰巧經過 送上奇異花朵 <br />\n樣子不錯 也不失 也不過<br />\n將孤單的我 帶入了幻覺<br />\n<br />\n如果 荒島中有你伴我蹉跎 可算不枉<br />\n好好抱月光 將今天痛快活過一趟 把死也淡看<br />\n曠野中拾荒 儘管知道這事態骯髒 還任由愛盛放<br />\n也許這生物都很脆弱到周遭要寄託<br />\n逃避過 來換新的軀殼<br />\n<br />\n轉眼已走很遠 跌進無盡深淵<br />\n互取溫暖 帶不走 切不斷<br />\n多麼的繾綣 快活過便算<br />\n<br />\n如果 荒島中有你伴我蹉跎 可算不枉<br />\n好好抱月光 將今天痛快活過一趟 把死也淡看<br />\n曠野中拾荒 儘管知道這事態骯髒 還任由愛盛放<br />\n也許這生物都很脆弱到周遭要寄託<br />\n逃避過 來換新的軀殼<br />\n<br />\n活在想像最美好<br />\n浪漫化這一切可覆蓋糟糕<br />\n越是好 越怕最終得不到<br />\n才驚醒 才發覺已變做野草<br />\n<br />\n如果 當天可有發現這些錯 不再觸摸<br />\n把酒看月光 荒島中與你互相消磨 不死也是錯<br />\n暗裡渡陳倉 得到溫暖過後太坎坷 誰願來慰藉我<br />\n片刻的歡樂竟可賭上了一世的罪惡<br />\n逃避過 留下一堆軀殼<br />\n<br />\n==========<br />\n<br />\n去歌<br />\n<br />\n陳蕾 Panther Chan - 荒島之幻象 Illusion Of A Desert Island (Official Music Video)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=coxeA969dGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcoxeA969dGQ&d=07YJri3FF82qzkXABTRKfJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=33baf0a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=coxeA969dGQ</a>"},{"pid":"073c1229fce3a6e8a7bcbb2ba158c1720e2fe603","tid":2482022,"uid":54658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"吹奏吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aab5d7f90b8b23bcd2ff125df4f559c74b4ace6","tid":2482022,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3f5400236eb8ff30104dc99510fa25348aa548","tid":2482022,"uid":38277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"豹哥好野"},{"pid":"4d908d9f4085a3a30210f90e3852f4720416956f","tid":2482022,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kfs.io/playlist/global/58424311v42/cropresize/300x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kfs.io%2Fplaylist%2Fglobal%2F58424311v42%2Fcropresize%2F300x300.jpg&h=6eaadb92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7627f3e1fa8f64045aa06c2eb0dbc48d29b46946","tid":2482022,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/S5dNpFd2aiU/mqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=